title: KULTDASHIANS
description: Feast your ears on the first ever Bitch Sesh/Deep Dive crossover ep! Queens Danielle Schneider and Jessica St. Clair are away and the mice they will play! Casey and June Diane Raphael "dive deep" into The Deep End (The Teal Swan doc on Hulu) and do anything but "bitch" during their "sesh" about The Kardashians. See how fun this is already?? ENJOY!
author: bwordsesh@gmail.com (Earwolf)
